	(text_box "!!! CAUTION !!!\n\nVDD3 must remain between 3.3V and 5.5V.\n\nOnly one power source should be connected at a time:\n    1. From the upstream board sockets via the mainboard.\n    2. From the ISP socket.\n    3. From the USB-to-serial converter socket."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
